column5: Does anyone have a set of the old school lawn darts kicking around that they would be willing to part with? You know the dangerous ones that had sharp points and stuck in the grass. Looking for a full set with the rings,been trying since last summer to hunt a set down. thanks
Good luck, ive been looking for a while lol
well if you get a line on a second set ....please pass it along and I will do the same
Likely easier to buy a shotgun. Man, they were fun.
Pretty pricey joey but its certainly an option, thank you.
Build a cornhole game. Just as much funv
